# üöÄ **Convert to Transformers Format**

After training your TPU v4-8 JAX/Flax weights, use:

```python
from transformers import Phi3ForCausalLM, Phi3Config

config = Phi3Config()
model = Phi3ForCausalLM(config)
model.load_state_dict(torch.load("phi3_tpu_v4.bin"))
model.save_pretrained("./hf-phi3")
tokenizer.save_pretrained("./hf-phi3")
```

Upload to HuggingFace:

```bash
huggingface-cli upload hf-phi3 --repo myusername/phi3-1b-malay
```

